  <section class="callout">
    <strong>Abstract:</strong> Acne is primarily an immune-mediated response to Neu5Gc (from red meat and dairy) and gluten (from wheat and related grains). Chronic immune activation leads to skin inflammation and acne as a visible manifestation of systemic immune processes.
  </section>

